NOMBRE / PAQUETE DEL APLICATIVO ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    PAQUETE
        android/app/build.gradle  →   applicationId = "pe.igest.app"
                                      namespace     = "pe.igest.app"
    NOMBRE_APP
        pubspec.yaml                                →   name: igest_app
        android/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml    →   android:label="iGEST"
    IMPORTANTE! Verificar/Cambiar este archivo: android\app\src\main\kotlin\com\example\igest_app\MainActivity.kt 
        package com.example.igest_app               →   package pe.igest.app 

VERSIONES ANDROID-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    android/app/build.gradle  →   

        defaultConfig {
            ...
            //minSdk = flutter.minSdkVersion
            minSdk = 30
            //targetSdk = flutter.targetSdkVersion
            targetSdk = 36
            ...
        }

* En Android Studio Instalar previamente NDK, Command Line, cMake, Google USB Driver

